node.title: Person hospitalised with critical injuries after incident at Christchurch carwash
node.content: ["A person has been critically injured in an incident at a carwash facility in Christchurch.", "Police say they were notified of an incident at an automated carwash facility in Ferrymead, Christchurch just after 10:10am on Friday.", "One person received critical injuries in the incident and has been transported to hospital.\u00a0", "Police have launched an investigation and WorkSafe has been advised.\u00a0"]
